                    <span>The boxing register is a must have for any true boxing fanatic.  The book has information of every inductee from the IBHOF, from the pioneers of the bare-knuckle era to "The Greatest", all of them have at least a page dedicated to them in the great book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">rock em....then sock em...</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      /
